The paper deals with a computer vision problem of recognizing font styles from images of text, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes the use of deep neural networks, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses domain adaptation, which is a technique used to transfer knowledge from one domain to another, and this falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with image data, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
